"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-music-music-news-lady-gaga-2024-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-1235067899\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByLarisha Paul  TheParis Olympicsare officially underway, andLady Gagalit the event's musical torch with a rousing performance on the River Seine at the opening ceremony Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga brought high-level camp to the River Seine, kicking off her appearance with a performance of the French song \\\"Mon Truc En Plume\\\" by Zizi Jeanmaire.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zizi Jeanmaire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singer emerged from a cluster of pink feathers, dancing on a gold staircase in a chic black ensemble.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her performance channeled Jeanmaire's appearance on theEd Sullivan Showin January 1965.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 496, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Sullivan\", \"score\": 0.9999999998817657, \"rank\": 1.1807649049214413e-10, \"text\": \"Sullivan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Sullivan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Sullivan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga was backed by a full band - including an enthusiastic horn section - plus a full crew of dancers.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in true Gaga fashion - literally - she used a minor costume change to note a change in the set.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she moved to sit at the piano, the band paused for a moment while she played.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When her dancers came back over, their pink feather shields covered her for a moment before she re-emerged, wearing a back piece covered in a poof of white feathers.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lady Gaga performing \\\"Mon truc en plumes\\\" at the#Olympicsopening ceremony!pic.twitter.com/a1WOKzn2AV  Gaga shared her gratitude for performing at theOlympicson an X post on Friday, saying the moment with the Jeanmarie track was full-circle since Jeanmarie starred in Cole Porter's \\\"Anything Goes,\\\" Gaga's first jazz release.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I am not a French artist, I have always felt a very special connection with French people and singing French music-I wanted nothing more than to create a performance that would warm the heart of France, celebrate French art and music, and on such a momentous occasion remind everyone of one of the most magical cities on earth-Paris,\\\" Gaga wrote.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999860810031, \"rank\": 8.798264027240784e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga also shared that they rented pom poms from the cabaret theater Le Lido, collaborated with Dior for custom costumes, and used naturally molted feathers for her looks.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I studied French choreography that put a modern twist on a French classic,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French classic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Classic_Races\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I rehearsed tirelessly to study a joyful French dance, brushing up on some old skills-I bet you did not know I used to dance at a 60's French party on the lower east side when I was first starting out!\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Editor's picksThe 250 Greatest Albums of the 21st Century So FarThe 100 Best TV Episodes of All TimeThe 500 Greatest Albums of All Time100 Best Movies of the 21st Century  I feel so completely grateful to have been asked to open the Paris@Olympics2024 this year.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also humbled to be asked by the Olympics organizing committee to sing such a special French song-a song to honor the French people and their tremendous history of art, music, and\\u2026pic.twitter.com/FMNyiosHUR  \\\"I hope you love this performance as much as I do.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9890492783964526, \"rank\": 0.010275511446115888, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2509, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And to everyone in France, thank you so much for welcoming me to your country to sing in honor of you-it's a gift I will never forget!\\\"\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999860810031, \"rank\": 8.798264027240784e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga wrote.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2786, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congratulations to all the athletes who are competing in this year's Olympic Games!\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is my supreme honor to sing for you and cheer you on!!\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching the Olympic Games always makes me cry!\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your talent is unimaginable.\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let the games begin!\\\"\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga's appearance comes after the singer beganteasingher upcoming musical era.\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just me in the studio-happy as ever making music,\\\" she wrote on Instagram earlier this month.\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3185, \"end\": 3194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.949793620096121e-37, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Feel so grateful, heart is peaceful.\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like meditation.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait for you to hear what I am working on.\\\"\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the premiere of her concert filmGaga Chromatica Ball, she described the music as being \\\"nothing like anything that I have ever made before.\\\"\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her most recent album,Chromatica, arrived in 2020.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3495, \"end\": 3505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chromatica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chromatica\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chromatica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chromatica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The musician recently wrapped a brief run of shows at Dolby Live at Park MGM in Las Vegas.\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3605, \"end\": 3614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9943458690097798, \"rank\": 0.0056862817779651745, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performances were part of a revival of Gaga's Jazz and Piano show celebrating jazz standards and tracks from the Great American songbook.Trending StoriesJohn Lithgow Knows J.K. Rowling's Anti-Trans Views Will Now Forever Come Up in 'Every Interview'Kevin Spacey's 'Mental Illness' Should Trigger $29.5 Million Payout, 'House of Cards' Trial Jurors HearBTS Nails Its Comeback With 'Arirang'Top Disaster Response Official Claims He Teleported to a Waffle House  The2024 Summer Olympicswill run from July 26 through Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 4141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.475449037693627e-32, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 3739, \"end\": 3747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999153681368416, \"rank\": 8.45505212020219